generic:link.msg:message: "Amount of fund Transfer" = (Amount of intrabank + interbank fund transfer)
"Amount of interbank fund transfer" = summation of fund transfer from (NEFT, RTGS, IMPS, UPI, E - Wallets, Micro ATM (POS), ATM and Others)
"Amount of payment of goods & services" = (Amount of intrabank + Interbank payment of goods & services)
"Number of fund transfer" = (Number of intrabank + interbank fund transfer)
"Number of interbank fund transfer" summation of fund transfer from (NEFT, RTGS, IMPS, UPI, E - Wallets, Micro ATM (POS), ATM and Others)
"Number of payment of goods & services" = (Number of intrabank + Interbank payment of goods & services)
Total remittances amount is sum of its child elements.
Total remittances number is sum of its child elements.
